query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(a1 q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) NoMergeJoin(a1 b q1 s t1 tq1 u1 acc) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('algebraic-topology',
'analytic-geometry',
'approximation',
'category-theory',
'combinations',
'complex-numbers',
'elementary-number-theory',
'field-theory',
'galois-theory',
'geometry',
'lp-spaces',
'partial-derivative',
'predicate-logic',
'pyqgis',
'r')
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('drupal',
'gis',
'math')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND u1.downvotes >= 10 AND u1.downvotes <= 100000
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Benefactor',
'Guru',
'Peer Pressure',
'Suffrage',
'Tag Editor',
'Tumbleweed')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
